      <title>翻转比特的踪迹：AES-GCM在可信执行环境中的致命漏洞</title>
      <link>https://qife122.github.io/p/%E7%BF%BB%E8%BD%AC%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E7%9A%84%E8%B8%AA%E8%BF%B9aes-gcm%E5%9C%A8%E5%8F%AF%E4%BF%A1%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E8%87%B4%E5%91%BD%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E/</link>
